'''Museum board''' is a type of [[paperboard]]. Specifically, it is a white, [[Acid-free paper|acid free]] cardboard that bends fairly easily in one direction but is fairly stiff in the other, due to the grain of the paper fibers.<ref>http://en.wikibooks.org/wiki/Bookbinding/Museum_board</ref>

